**Professional Profile**
An aspiring Information Technology professional with foundational project-based experience across web development, system administration, and network security. Though possessing 0 years of formal professional experience, the candidate has successfully completed several intensive course projects. These include designing and securing WiFi networks, developing a full-stack gym system with C# and .NET Core, and configuring SharePoint and network systems. This demonstrates a strong practical understanding of diverse IT domains and a proactive approach to skill development.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Key technical proficiencies include Computer Networking, System Administration, Network Security, and Network Design. The candidate is also skilled in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, C#, .NET Core, MVC, SQL Server, Git, and VMware.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a degree in Information Technology, specializing in Computer Networks and Data Communication, from Tôn Đức Thắng University, with an anticipated graduation in 2025. Complementary certifications include Agile Development & Scrum and an Aptis ESOL Certificate – Level B1. An Ethical Hacker on Cisco certification is also anticipated in 2025.